<p>Varhadi is a dialect of <a href="/wiki/Marathi_language" title="Marathi language">Marathi</a> spoken in <a href="/wiki/Vidarbha" title="Vidarbha">Vidarbha</a> region of <a href="/wiki/Maharashtra" title="Maharashtra">Maharashtra</a> and by Marathi people of adjoining parts of Madhya Pradesh, Chhattisgarh &amp; Andhra Pradesh states of India.</p>
<table id="toc" class="toc">
<tr>
<td>
